  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1: 5 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 7 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Serial firing: 7 killed in 5 days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nationwide, 7 people have died in shooting incidents from the 27th to today (31).",
        "The police said that two people were killed in the shooting incidents in Kotanchenai and Rathgama areas yesterday and the day before yesterday.",
        "A 51-year-old man was killed on Saturday (30) night when two unidentified men on a motorcycle opened fire on Kotanchenai Vivekananda Road.",
        "One person was shot dead and two others were injured in a firing incident that took place today (31) in Rathgama, Kammategoda area under Galle police division.",
        "Rathgama police said that two people who were traveling on a motorcycle shot at them with Ri-56 rifles and escaped, while one person was seriously injured and admitted to the hospital and died.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 45-year-old resident of Rathgama, Thevenikoda.",
        "The injured have been identified as 47 and 29 years old and the Rathgama police are conducting further investigations into the incident.",
        "Meanwhile, five people were killed in separate shooting incidents on the 27th and 28th in the areas of Gampaha, Ambalangodai and Rathmalanai.",
        "Saman Rohitha, a member of the underworld group known as 'Bus Pota', was seriously injured in a gunfight in front of the Gampaha Magistrate's Court on the afternoon of 27th, and another died that evening and two days later.",
        "Two people were killed in a gunfight on the evening of 27th at a funeral ceremony held in Kalakoda area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda.",
        "In this case, the police said that a 30-year-old man was killed in a shooting by two men who entered a house in Rathmalan, Silva Mawatha area in the early hours of the 28th."
      ],
